high_descs: turn right then walk straight then turn right again and walk straight towards the counter then turn left and walk straight then left again at the green table
pick up the knife next to the spoon on the table
turn left walk straight a tiny bit then left again and walk towards the sink
put the knife into the sink and fill the sink with water and then drain the sink and remove the knife from the water
turn around and look up at the green table
put the knife back onto the green table
anns.task_desc: Clean the knife in the sink and put it back on the table

high_descs: Turn around, go to the stove, turn left, go to the green table on the left, face the potatoes on the table.
Pick up the yellow knife on the table.
Turn around, bring the knife to the sink.
Stand the knife in the sink on its end, wash the knife with water.
Take the cleaned knife in the sink, turn around, go to the green table.
Stand the knife on the table in front of the front fork.
anns.task_desc: Stand a cleaned knife on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go back, then left around the island and face it on the left.
Pick up the knife from the far side of the island.
Hold the knife and turn around to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink, turn on the water and off again. Pick up the knife from the sink.
Hold the knife and turn around to the island.
Place the knife on the island, in the front center.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a knife and place it on the counter.
